{"title_page": "Latvians", "text_new": "{{short description|Ethnic group}}\n{{About|the ethnic group called Latvians or Letts|the inhabitants of [[Latvia]]|Demographics of Latvia}}\n{{Infobox ethnic group\n| group = Latvians\n| native_name = latvie\u0161i\n| native_name_lang = \n| image = Latvian song festival by Dainis Matisons, 2008.jpg\n| image_caption = Participants of the [[Latvian Song and Dance Festival]] in Latvian folk costumes\n| population = {{circa}} '''1.6\u20131.7 million'''\n| popplace = {{flag|Latvia}} 1,229,067 <small>(2014)</small><ref>{{cite web|url=http://data.csb.gov.lv/pxweb/lv/Sociala/Sociala__ikgad__iedz__iedzskaits/IS0080.px/table/tableViewLayout1/?rxid=cdcb978c-22b0-416a-aacc-aa650d3e2ce0|title=ISG08. Latvie\u0161u skaits Latvij\u0101 un R\u012bg\u0101 gada s\u0101kum\u0101|website=Data.csb.gov.lv|accessdate=2017-08-02}}{{Dead link|date=February 2020 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n<center>{{small|Other significant population centers:}}</center>\n| region1 = {{flag|United Kingdom}}\n| pop1 = 102,000 <small>(2014)</small><ref>[http://www.statistics.gov.uk/statbase/Product.asp?vlnk=15147 Population by country of birth and nationality], Annual Population Survey, Office of National Statistics, 2014] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100828161544/http://www.statistics.gov.uk/statbase/Product.asp?vlnk=15147 |date=August 28, 2010 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=BNS |url=http://www.tvnet.lv/zinas/arvalstis/381303-lielbritanija_paslaik_dzivo_39_tukstosi_viesstradnieku_no_latvijas |title=TVNET :: \u0100rvalst\u012bs - Lielbrit\u0101nij\u0101 pa\u0161laik dz\u012bvo 39 t\u016bksto\u0161i viesstr\u0101dnieku no Latvijas |publisher=Tvnet.lv |date= |accessdate=2011-12-03}}</ref>\n| region2 = {{flag|United States}}\n| pop2 = 96,070\u2013102,000 <small>(2009)</small><ref>{{cite web|url=http://factfinder.census.gov/servlet/DTTable?_bm=y&-ds_name=ACS_2009_1YR_G00_&-mt_name=ACS_2009_1YR_G2000_B04003&-CONTEXT=dt&-redoLog=true&